{"lang": "zh_TW", "eventid": "main_14", "eventName": "慈悲燈塔", "entryType": "MAINLINE", "storyCode": "14-19", "avgTag": "行動前", "storyName": "晶簇之內", "storyInfo": "博士在未知的地方醒來，陪在身邊的卻是普瑞賽斯。\n", "storyList": [{"id": 0, "prop": "HEADER", "attributes": {"key": "title_test", "is_skippable": "true", "fit_mode": "BLACK_MASK"}}, {"id": 1, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 2, "prop": "stopmusic", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 3, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 4, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "bg_abyss_1", "screenadapt": "coverall", "xScale": 1.08, "yScale": 1.08, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 5, "prop": "focusout", "attributes": {"duration": 0.5, "type": "bg", "from": 0.0, "to": 1.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 6, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 7, "prop": "PlayMusic", "attributes": {"key": "$babel_loop", "volume": 0.8}}, {"id": 8, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 1.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 9, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 0.5}}, {"id": 10, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你可能記不清今天對你來說，究竟意味著什麼。"}}, {"id": 11, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "這會讓你陷入十分危險的處境。"}}, {"id": 12, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……"}}, {"id": 13, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "不。"}}, {"id": 14, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你必須想起來。"}}, {"id": 15, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 16, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 17, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 1.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 18, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 19, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "bg_black", "screenadapt": "coverall", "block": "true"}}, {"id": 20, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 0.5}}, {"id": 21, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.5, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 22, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……狀態……正常……", "name": "模糊的聲音"}}, {"id": 23, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……抱歉……", "name": "模糊的聲音"}}, {"id": 24, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "又讓你受苦了。", "name": "模糊的聲音"}}, {"id": 25, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 26, "prop": "stopmusic", "attributes": {"fadetime": 2.0}}, {"id": 27, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 28, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 1.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 29, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 30, "prop": "Image", "attributes": {"image": "avg_8_9", "screenadapt": "coverall"}}, {"id": 31, "prop": "focusout", "attributes": {"duration": 0.5, "type": "cg", "from": 0.0, "to": 1.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 32, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 33, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 34, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……", "name": "？？？"}}, {"id": 35, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "博士，抓緊我的手。", "name": "？？？"}}, {"id": 36, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "下次請不要再一聲不響地離開我了。", "name": "？？？"}}, {"id": 37, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 38, "prop": "focusout", "attributes": {"duration": 1.5, "type": "cg", "from": 1.0, "to": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 39, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 0.5}}, {"id": 40, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你也不會再接受這種事了，對吧？", "name": "？？？"}}, {"id": 41, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "嗯……怎麼了，Dr.{@nickname}……", "name": "？？？"}}, {"id": 42, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "為什麼要用這麼陌生的眼神看著我？", "name": "？？？"}}, {"id": 43, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 44, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 45, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 1.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 46, "prop": "bgeffect", "attributes": {"name": "$eb_dim_openeye", "layer": 1.0}}, {"id": 47, "prop": "image", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 48, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 49, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "bg_abyss_1", "screenadapt": "coverall", "xScale": 1.08, "yScale": 1.08, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 50, "prop": "focusout", "attributes": {"duration": 0.1, "type": "bg", "from": 1.0, "to": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 51, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_083"}}, {"id": 52, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 53, "prop": "playMusic", "attributes": {"intro": "$mist_intro", "key": "$mist_loop", "volume": 0.6}}, {"id": 54, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 55, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.0}}, {"id": 56, "prop": "bgeffect", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 57, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_083", "focus": "n"}}, {"id": 58, "prop": "Decision", "attributes": {"options": "（“未知語言”）普瑞……賽斯……？", "values": "1"}, "targetLine": {"option1": "line59"}}, {"id": 59, "prop": "Predicate", "attributes": {"references": "1"}, "endOfOpt": false}, {"id": 60, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_083", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 61, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "欸，你又從哪裡學來了這麼奇怪的語言？", "name": "普瑞賽斯"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_083"}, {"id": 62, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "這次休眠你又偷偷將思維上傳到某個旋臂末端的文明中了嗎？", "name": "普瑞賽斯"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_083"}, {"id": 63, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "好了，再確認一下你的語言功能恢復得如何。", "name": "普瑞賽斯"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_083"}, {"id": 64, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "別說你睡了一場大覺，連我的名字都忘了。", "name": "普瑞賽斯"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_083"}, {"id": 65, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "來，再叫一次我的名字，數據庫會分析你的所有聲音數據。", "name": "普瑞賽斯"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_083"}, {"id": 66, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 67, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_083", "focus": "n"}}, {"id": 68, "prop": "Decision", "attributes": {"options": "普瑞……賽斯……", "values": "1"}, "targetLine": {"option1": "line69"}}, {"id": 69, "prop": "Predicate", "attributes": {"references": "1"}, "endOfOpt": false}, {"id": 70, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_083", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 71, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "恢復得很快嘛，{@nickname}。", "name": "普瑞賽斯"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_083"}, {"id": 72, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "但是你的身體剛剛復甦，還沒有完全適應。", "name": "普瑞賽斯"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_083"}, {"id": 73, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "急著亂動的話，小心NX-07把你按回床鋪哦。它新換的指令很難解開，就連我都愛莫能助。", "name": "普瑞賽斯"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_083"}, {"id": 74, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 75, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_083", "focus": "n"}}, {"id": 76, "prop": "Decision", "attributes": {"options": "你……我在哪裡？", "values": "1"}, "targetLine": {"option1": "line77"}}, {"id": 77, "prop": "Predicate", "attributes": {"references": "1"}, "endOfOpt": false}, {"id": 78, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_083", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 79, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "當然還在“羅德島”，我們的家。", "name": "普瑞賽斯"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_083"}, {"id": 80, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 81, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_083", "focus": "n"}}, {"id": 82, "prop": "Decision", "attributes": {"options": "只有……我一個人？;羅德島的……其他人呢……", "values": "1;2"}, "targetLine": {"option1": "line83", "option2": "line83"}}, {"id": 83, "prop": "Predicate", "attributes": {"references": "1;2"}, "endOfOpt": false, "targetLine": "line87"}, {"id": 84, "prop": "Predicate", "attributes": {"references": "1"}, "endOfOpt": true}, {"id": 85, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_083", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 86, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "怎麼會只有你呢？我也在這裡呀。", "name": "普瑞賽斯"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_083"}, {"id": 87, "prop": "Predicate", "attributes": {"references": "2"}, "endOfOpt": true}, {"id": 88, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_083", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 89, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……你果然還是會這樣問。", "name": "普瑞賽斯"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_083"}, {"id": 90, "prop": "Predicate", "attributes": {"references": "1;2"}}, {"id": 91, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "變故發生得很快。防禦矩陣損傷超過了百分之九十，受極端環境影響，修理單元也很難在短時間內恢復工作。", "name": "普瑞賽斯"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_083"}, {"id": 92, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "在你休眠後不久，許多同事就相繼離開了這裡……大家都很珍惜這星星墜落之前的時間，我很理解。", "name": "普瑞賽斯"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_083"}, {"id": 93, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "現在，的確只有我們兩個了。當然，AMa-10也還在，而且精神很好，很活潑。", "name": "普瑞賽斯"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_083"}, {"id": 94, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "別擔心，羅德島剩下的部分還可以維繫基本功能，我們還有一點時間。", "name": "普瑞賽斯"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_083"}, {"id": 95, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "{@nickname}，你在我身邊的時候，我並不害怕結局。", "name": "普瑞賽斯"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_083"}, {"id": 96, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "無論是構成我們身體的物質崩毀，我們的意識停止變化，還是宇宙的法則顛倒，我都可以坦然接受。", "name": "普瑞賽斯"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_083"}, {"id": 97, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "只要你還在我身邊就夠了。", "name": "普瑞賽斯"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_083"}, {"id": 98, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 99, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_083", "focus": "n"}}, {"id": 100, "prop": "Decision", "attributes": {"options": "……", "values": "1"}, "targetLine": {}}, {"id": 101, "prop": "Predicate", "attributes": {"references": "1"}}, {"id": 102, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_083", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 103, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你還在出神，是還沒從夢裡醒來嗎，{@nickname}？", "name": "普瑞賽斯"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_083"}, {"id": 104, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 105, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_cloakmovement", "volume": 1.0}}, {"id": 106, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.5}}, {"id": 107, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_083", "focus": "n"}}, {"id": 108, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "她握著你的手，貼在了自己的臉頰上。"}}, {"id": 109, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "肌膚的觸感溫暖而真實，將你從夢裡拉回現實。"}}, {"id": 110, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_083", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 111, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "如果是這樣，我想知道你的夢。", "name": "普瑞賽斯"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_083"}, {"id": 112, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "不過，裡面最好有我。", "name": "普瑞賽斯"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_083"}, {"id": 113, "prop": "stopmusic", "attributes": {"fadetime": 2.0}}, {"id": 114, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 115, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 116, "prop": "Decision", "attributes": {"options": "……;……夢嗎……？;……很長的夢嗎……？", "values": "1;2;3"}, "targetLine": {}}, {"id": 117, "prop": "Predicate", "attributes": {"references": "1;2;3"}}, {"id": 118, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 119, "prop": "focusout", "attributes": {"duration": 2.0, "type": "bg", "from": 0.0, "to": 1.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 120, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 121, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 122, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 123, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 124, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 125, "prop": "cameraEffect", "attributes": {"effect": "Grayscale", "keep": "true", "amount": 0.8, "fadetime": 0.0}}, {"id": 126, "prop": "Image", "attributes": {"image": "avg_9_2", "x": 50.0, "y": 30.0, "xScale": 1.15, "yScale": 1.15, "fadetime": 0.0}}, {"id": 127, "prop": "focusout", "attributes": {"duration": 0.1, "type": "cg", "from": 0.0, "to": 1.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 128, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 129, "prop": "PlayMusic", "attributes": {"key": "$memory_loop", "volume": 0.6}}, {"id": 130, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 1.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 131, "prop": "focusout", "attributes": {"duration": 1.5, "type": "cg", "from": 1.0, "to": 0.0, "block": "false"}}, {"id": 132, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.0}}, {"id": 133, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "“泰拉”。"}}, {"id": 134, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "那片大地……天災……礦石病……"}}, {"id": 135, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "可你已經漫步在那片大地上數年，一切都如此真實。"}}, {"id": 136, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 137, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 138, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 1.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 139, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 140, "prop": "cameraEffect", "attributes": {"effect": "Grayscale", "keep": "true", "amount": 0.8, "fadetime": 0.0}}, {"id": 141, "prop": "Image", "attributes": {"image": "avg_8_15", "screenadapt": "coverall"}}, {"id": 142, "prop": "focusout", "attributes": {"duration": 0.1, "type": "bg", "from": 1.0, "to": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 143, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 0.5}}, {"id": 144, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 1.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 145, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 146, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "人群的歡呼依舊在你耳邊迴盪。"}}, {"id": 147, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "天災不曾摧毀希望，在苦難的創傷下，你依然可以觸碰那恆久的餘溫。"}}, {"id": 148, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "溫暖的。動人的。你被包圍在溫柔的人群之中……"}}, {"id": 149, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "“羅德島”。"}}, {"id": 150, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你永遠不會忘記的羅德島。"}}, {"id": 151, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "治癒過你傷痕的羅德島……曾留下過遺憾的羅德島……"}}, {"id": 152, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你不是依然站在這裡嗎？"}}, {"id": 153, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 154, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 155, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 1.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 156, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "和他們一起，你去過冰雪覆蓋之地。"}}, {"id": 157, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 158, "prop": "image", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 159, "prop": "cameraEffect", "attributes": {"effect": "Grayscale", "keep": "true", "amount": 0.8, "fadetime": 0.0}}, {"id": 160, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "24_g1_snowyforest", "screenadapt": "coverall", "block": "true"}}, {"id": 161, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 0.5}}, {"id": 162, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 1.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 163, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.0}}, {"id": 164, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 165, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 166, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 1.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 167, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "也感受過沙灘的柔軟。"}}, {"id": 168, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 169, "prop": "image", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 170, "prop": "cameraEffect", "attributes": {"effect": "Grayscale", "keep": "true", "amount": 0.8, "fadetime": 0.0}}, {"id": 171, "prop":